    "text": "Anna: Some trees have age rings."
  },
  {
    "start": 206.44,
    "end": 209.959,
    "text": "Anna: The age rings tell the age of the tree."
  },
  {
    "start": 209.959,
    "end": 213.879,
    "text": "Anna: This part of the tree has six age rings"
  },
  {
    "start": 214.64,
    "end": 217.92,
    "text": "Anna: So this part of the tree is six years old."
  },
  {
    "start": 217.92,
    "end": 221.2,
    "text": "Anna: Maybe Max has age rings!"
